blockquote><br />\n我見識小 未見過有人鐘意著bikini行山"},{"pid":"14f100cc612ded559291a619e23255565cf44456","tid":200281,"uid":105945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T21:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢位豬閪邊撚個黎？唔識佢<br />\n行山著成咁無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好乜撚都屌啦</blockquote><br />\n我見識小 未見過有人鐘意著bikini行山</blockquote><br />\n佢係著真bikini加拖鞋行<br />\n之前蘋果有片<br />\n咁都無問題?"},{"pid":"c8684ce1ccbe42b570d04d8d693a341fbb506e75","tid":200281,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T22:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢位豬閪邊撚個黎？唔識佢<br />\n行山著成咁無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好乜撚都屌啦</blockquote><br />\n我見識小 未見過有人鐘意著bikini行山</blockquote><br />\n佢係著真bikini加拖鞋行<br />\n之前蘋果有片<br />\n咁都無問題?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前教人去郊外要著淺色長袖衫褲，依家就鼓吹埋啲咁嘅風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係野外有咩野事都可以有件衫擋一擋。仲有，唔好呀豬呀狗都加 女神 上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed1e1a6e6dc0bf7642b08c3b19c1969cd2a2b27","tid":200281,"uid":17052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T23:47:39.000Z","msg":"我唔行山但記得好耐之前個訪問話鍾意著拖鞋行我就覺得好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5c3ed17c7f64f984f5db2e797de61f04773f77","tid":200281,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T23:49:51.000Z","msg":"佢最撚核突嗰下係要扮晒教人行山，享受行山樂趣，搵錢就搵錢啦臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a7645e4d03ec74dbc3983f1163565e9567aa85","tid":200281,"uid":105945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T00:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢最撚核突嗰下係要扮晒教人行山，享受行山樂趣，搵錢就搵錢啦臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁唸<br />\n我真心唔明白點解會有人覺得行山著bratop正常<br />\n我唔知佢地會唔會最後話其實tanya wong著bikini都係適合行山<br />\n叫我唔好係度搞事<br />\n咁多蚊咬 咁多植物可能界傷你 點樣行呀<br />\n佢自己話係行難行的山路<br />\n唔係一般大路<br />\n我真係唔明點樣著bratop去行<br />\n<br />\n其實搵錢不是問題<br />\n但你起碼自己要真係鐘意行山 識得行山<br />\n而唔係好似佢咁<br />\n純粹為左上報 推廣自己而行<br />\n搞個網全部資料都係copy<br />\n仲要全部都錯<br />\n你究竟點樣大學畢業<br />\n基本research skill都無<br />\n你點寫essay呀<br />\n<br />\n都唔講仲要為左吸引狗公去扮單身<br />\n將所有Facebook ig的情侶相delete哂"},{"pid":"b9482ee6dfd06315fc5f2634bcb69fb860f5345d","tid":200281,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"生嘢女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dad57656ab4cdb3db376e99da455af692a0372","tid":200281,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:02:12.000Z","msg":"不如除晒佢啦"},{"pid":"fc5a68d3056b420e8a7c5f22827792e5bec65ebf","tid":200281,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ebc6a9f9b6275ef0ada8dab8fcfa3f04811e51","tid":200281,"uid":37259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:11:11.000Z","msg":"聽到佢把聲都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffaae40df3e38639a5abf991d39bc93460593b2","tid":200281,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"呢條女真係食屎狗9up當秘級<br />\n污染成個山頭"},{"pid":"286001838e0c81f66836b2638ee356e50b6d1034","tid":200281,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />豬行山"},{"pid":"d74778c008165f537509e84e504d3bb5f875ce67","tid":200281,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"佢想做第二個肥瓜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/